[% title = "Password recovery" %]

<p>You can request a password recovery link to your email address.
When you click it you can set a new password for your account.</p>

<form method="post" action="[% recover_url %]">
    <input type="email" name="email" value="[% email | html %]" placeholder="email address">
    <input type="submit" value="Send recovery link">
</form>
